Question: All images show dogs in snowy scenes, and one image includes a florward-facing dog with a face-full of snow.

Reference Answer: False

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show dogs in snowy scenes?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image show dogs in snowy scenes?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image include a forward-facing dog with a face-full of snow?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image include a forward-facing dog with a face-full of snow?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER2} xor {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} and {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
